  "title": "chore(dependencies): deduplicate devDependencies",
  "body": "We have some duplicate dependencies since the migrations. This PR decreases that from a total of 3.5 to 3.1 GB, as it's fairly hard to find out what's duplicate and what will have the most impact.\r\n\r\nWhat I've done:\r\n- harmonise `@babel/core`\r\n- harmonise `prop-types`\r\n- moved webpack dependency for example building to its own \"package\"\r\n- harmonise webpack versions using resolutions",
